body:
In todays listing of new CPAN modules, there was one called constants,
http://search.cpan.org/~hooo/constants-0.0027/ . The synopsis reads;

        use constants;

EXPORTS

        UNDEF = undef;

        NO = defined;

        YES = !NO;

End of synopsis!


Could someone enlighten me as why (and how) you would use this module?


TIA



Owen

